univention-system-info (0.1.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * set write access for www-data to upload directory
  * add UCS version information to archive
  * download link to archive is now relative without the server name
  * do not UUID on XEN instance for unique identifier; instead the MAC
    address is used.
  * system-info-upload.py: the sender of the mail can now be set via a UCR
    variable (Bug #8969)

 -- Andreas Büsching <buesching@univention.de>  Fri,  9 Oct 2009 10:55:29 +0200

